{"tid":2443841,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"輝瑞疫苗在以色列錄得97%的防禦效率","createTime":"2021-03-12T09:51:45.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-14T08:15:52.000Z","uid":38861,"like":59,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"0848fa3805f9dd2653d5c37daedbb555810fc3f8","tid":2443841,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T09:51:45.000Z","msg":"Source:<a href=\"https://www.reuters.com/article/us-health-coronavirus-pfizer-israel-idUSKBN2B31IJ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-health-coronavirus-pfizer-israel-idUSKBN2B31IJ&d=RGPktlJYpqjIeXpZRAkgw1Ln0p5rLcPQxw7X33U7JQw%3D&h=72957cd1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-health-coronavirus-pfizer-israel-idUSKBN2B31IJ&h=9d42c268\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reuters.com/article/us-health-coronavirus-pfizer-israel-idUSKBN2B31IJ</a><br />\n<br />\n收集1月17日至3月6日從以色列得來的數據，輝瑞發現疫苗防禦武肺重症及死亡的效率達97%。<br />\n<br />\n數據收集其間，多達80%的測試樣本為英國變種（B.1.1.7.)，是為疫苗能抵擋英國變種的重要證據。<br />\n<br />\n而基於南非變種的樣本數量並不足夠，暫時未能斷定成效。<br />\n<br />\n資料尚未進行同行審查（Peer-reviewed)。<br />\n<br />\n科興及國藥直至現時尚未有正式公開第三期臨床報告，及公開應對變種的數據。"},{"pid":"2754990e6cb1d8c53573ef03a560059b9b3d34b9","tid":2443841,"uid":78892,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T09:52:46.000Z","msg":"USA<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cc24cc85d11d5d0be00f4fd79ae51a25b351ba5","tid":2443841,"uid":38861,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T09:53:59.000Z","msg":"而無症狀的感染，防禦率亦達94%，證明疫苗能有助阻截武肺傳播。"},{"pid":"862b255542d5754d3ab65e4af44f0b1462e8fb7c","tid":2443841,"uid":193642,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T09:54:45.000Z","msg":"以色列<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a34b77e6d13d3f39d93c34d3a536bac47b0f2c10","tid":2443841,"uid":14494,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-